snippet.textDisplay: Being vegetarian or vegan is easy. Just eat the same but substitute. I don’t like the false meats there is no good nutritional value in any of them quorn etc or veggie sausages. So for something like spag Bol just cool it exactly the same with lots of veg but use lentils instead of beef. Same for curries, change chicken for chickpeas . It doesn’t need to be tasteless and boring. I’ve just had my bloods taken and contrary to popular belief a vegan diet is high in iron! My iron levels are higher than my friend who was just told her levels are low and her diet is high in red and white meats. So please don’t believe all the crap you read on the internet! I don’t just eat green leaves 🤣 stuffed my face on the best toast dinner today with potatoes and parsnips but just had but roast instead! Was lush 👍
